    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"734814\">Dexin Zhang</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/287929-mathlib4/topic/Why.20Uncountable/near/571765602\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>And there are <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=%C2%AC+Countable+_\">some statements</a> on Borel spaces using <code>¬ Countable</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Alright, I think I'm convinced that this is a lack of API and not a lack of interesting results.</p>",
